    <item>
      <title>特朗普律师辩称选举案使前任总统面临刑事指控</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-09/trump-lawyers-argue-election-prosecution-opens-pandora-s-box</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普的律师告诉联邦上诉法院小组，因试图推翻 2020 年选举而起诉唐纳德·特朗普引发了人们的疑问，即其他前任总统是否可能因官方行为而受到刑事指控。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-09/trump-lawyers-argue-election-prosecution-opens-pandora-s-box</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 09 Jan 2024 15:13:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>数千人失去热量后普京将国防工厂国有化</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-09/putin-to-nationalize-defense-plant-after-thousands-lost-heat</link>
      <description><![CDATA[莫斯科附近地区州长表示，该工厂在寒冷天气下引发供暖故障，俄罗斯总统弗拉基米尔·普京下令将一家生产弹药的国防工厂国有化。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-09/putin-to-nationalize-defense-plant-after-thousands-lost-heat</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 09 Jan 2024 14:53:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>白宫召集气候顾问讨论液化天然气出口审批</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-09/white-house-assembles-climate-advisers-on-lng-export-approvals</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据称，拜登政府正在重新评估其在批准新的液化天然气出口设施时使用的气候标准，此举有可能在 2024 年大选临近时使悬而未决的项目陷入停滞。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-09/white-house-assembles-climate-advisers-on-lng-export-approvals</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 09 Jan 2024 14:46:33 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>到 2050 年，大电池可为英国电力系统节省高达 240 亿英镑</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-09/big-batteries-may-save-uk-power-system-up-to-24-billion-by-2050</link>
      <description><![CDATA[顾问公司 LCP Delta 表示，随着英国在推动海上风电扩张的过程中寻求可靠的备用电源，长期储能可以为英国电力系统节省数十亿英镑。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-09/big-batteries-may-save-uk-power-system-up-to-24-billion-by-2050</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 09 Jan 2024 14:11:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>布林肯、马克龙和李克强将出席达沃斯世界经济论坛</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-09/blinken-macron-li-headline-davos-forum-tackling-eroded-trust</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国国务卿安东尼·布林肯、法国总统埃马纽埃尔·马克龙和中国总理李强等全球知名人士将出席达沃斯世界经济论坛。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-09/blinken-macron-li-headline-davos-forum-tackling-eroded-trust</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 09 Jan 2024 14:09:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国丑闻中心前邮局老板重获荣誉</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-09/former-post-office-boss-at-center-of-uk-scandal-returns-honor</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国邮政局前首席执行官表示，在数百名员工被错误定为盗窃罪后，该组织遭到了强烈反对，她将归还以女王名义授予她的一项荣誉。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-09/former-post-office-boss-at-center-of-uk-scandal-returns-honor</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 09 Jan 2024 13:34:05 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>泰国采取行动禁止娱乐性使用大麻，阻碍新兴产业</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-09/thailand-moves-to-end-recreational-cannabis-use-in-setback-for-nascent-industry</link>
      <description><![CDATA[泰国提出一项新法案，提议禁止娱乐性使用大麻，并对违法者处以重罚，该法案旨在结束泰国成为亚洲第一个将大麻合法化的国家后的法律真空。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-09/thailand-moves-to-end-recreational-cannabis-use-in-setback-for-nascent-industry</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 09 Jan 2024 11:49:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>马克龙任命加布里埃尔·阿塔尔为法国最年轻总理</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-09/france-s-macron-taps-34-year-old-ally-attal-as-prime-minister</link>
      <description><![CDATA[距离欧洲议会选举仅几个月，法国总统埃马纽埃尔·马克龙任命一位 34 岁的盟友为法国总理，为他的政府带来新的动力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-09/france-s-macron-taps-34-year-old-ally-attal-as-prime-minister</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 09 Jan 2024 11:23:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>共同被告声称特朗普检察官有不正当恋情</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-09/trump-prosecutor-had-improper-relationship-co-defendant-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一份法庭文件称，亚特兰大地区检察官法尼·威利斯 (Fani Willis) 不当聘请一名浪漫伴侣，帮助起诉针对唐纳德·特朗普 (Donald Trump) 和其他 18 人的选举舞弊指控，后者是这位前总统的共同被告。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-09/trump-prosecutor-had-improper-relationship-co-defendant-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 09 Jan 2024 04:12:33 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普希望美国市场崩盘发生在拜登领导下，而不是他本人</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-09/trump-hopes-any-us-market-crash-happens-under-biden-and-not-him</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普表示，他希望美国经济崩溃发生在今年，而不是在他预期的第二任期内。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-09/trump-hopes-any-us-market-crash-happens-under-biden-and-not-him</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 09 Jan 2024 03:29:39 GMT</pubDate>
